instruction: Top 5 products by total ordered quantity.
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH p, sum(o.quantity) AS qty RETURN p.name, qty ORDER BY qty DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which supplier has the highest average lead time?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.lead_time) AS avg_lead RETURN s.name, avg_lead ORDER BY avg_lead DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: List top 3 suppliers by average delivery delay.
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.delay) AS avg_delay RETURN s.name, avg_delay ORDER BY avg_delay DESC LIMIT 3;

instruction: List warehouses where Product 'Widget' is stored.

instruction: Which transport mode has the highest average delay?

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.

instruction: Top 5 products by total ordered quantity.

instruction: Which supplier has the highest average lead time?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.lead_time) AS avg_lead RETURN s.name, avg_lead ORDER BY avg_lead DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Which suppliers are associated with the most delayed orders?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 0 WITH s, count(o) AS delayed RETURN s.name, delayed ORDER BY delayed DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which suppliers are associated with the most delayed orders?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 0 WITH s, count(o) AS delayed RETURN s.name, delayed ORDER BY delayed DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: List warehouses where Product 'Widget' is stored.
cypher: MATCH (p:Product {name:'Widget'})-[:STORED_AT]->(w:Warehouse) RETURN w.name;

instruction: Which transport mode has the highest average delay?
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) MATCH (sh)-[:TO_ORDER]->(o:CustomerOrder) WITH t, avg(o.delay) AS avg_delay RETURN t.name, avg_delay ORDER BY avg_delay DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which products are stored at WH_North?
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)-[:STORED_AT]->(w:Warehouse {name:'WH_North'}) RETURN p.name;

instruction: Count shipments by transport mode.
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) RETURN t.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Which suppliers are associated with the most delayed orders?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 0 WITH s, count(o) AS delayed RETURN s.name, delayed ORDER BY delayed DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which products are stored at WH_North?
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)-[:STORED_AT]->(w:Warehouse {name:'WH_North'}) RETURN p.name;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?

instruction: Which suppliers are associated with the most delayed orders?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 0 WITH s, count(o) AS delayed RETURN s.name, delayed ORDER BY delayed DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which transport mode has the highest average delay?
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) MATCH (sh)-[:TO_ORDER]->(o:CustomerOrder) WITH t, avg(o.delay) AS avg_delay RETURN t.name, avg_delay ORDER BY avg_delay DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Show orders delayed by more than 7 days.
cypher: MATCH (o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 7 RETURN o.id, o.delay ORDER BY o.delay DESC;

instruction: Top 5 products by total ordered quantity.
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH p, sum(o.quantity) AS qty RETURN p.name, qty ORDER BY qty DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which products are stored at WH_North?
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)-[:STORED_AT]->(w:Warehouse {name:'WH_North'}) RETURN p.name;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: List top 3 suppliers by average delivery delay.
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.delay) AS avg_delay RETURN s.name, avg_delay ORDER BY avg_delay DESC LIMIT 3;

instruction: List warehouses where Product 'Widget' is stored.

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which supplier has the highest average lead time?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.lead_time) AS avg_lead RETURN s.name, avg_lead ORDER BY avg_lead DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.

instruction: List warehouses where Product 'Widget' is stored.
cypher: MATCH (p:Product {name:'Widget'})-[:STORED_AT]->(w:Warehouse) RETURN w.name;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which suppliers are associated with the most delayed orders?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 0 WITH s, count(o) AS delayed RETURN s.name, delayed ORDER BY delayed DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which transport mode has the highest average delay?
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) MATCH (sh)-[:TO_ORDER]->(o:CustomerOrder) WITH t, avg(o.delay) AS avg_delay RETURN t.name, avg_delay ORDER BY avg_delay DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: List top 3 suppliers by average delivery delay.
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.delay) AS avg_delay RETURN s.name, avg_delay ORDER BY avg_delay DESC LIMIT 3;

instruction: List warehouses and their shipment counts, descending.
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Count shipments by transport mode.
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) RETURN t.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Which supplier has the highest average lead time?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH s, avg(o.lead_time) AS avg_lead RETURN s.name, avg_lead ORDER BY avg_lead DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Count shipments by transport mode.
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) RETURN t.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Show orders delayed by more than 7 days.
cypher: MATCH (o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 7 RETURN o.id, o.delay ORDER BY o.delay DESC;

instruction: Top 5 products by total ordered quantity.
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WITH p, sum(o.quantity) AS qty RETURN p.name, qty ORDER BY qty DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Which products are stored at WH_North?
cypher: MATCH (p:Product)-[:STORED_AT]->(w:Warehouse {name:'WH_North'}) RETURN p.name;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Which suppliers are associated with the most delayed orders?
cypher: MATCH (s:Supplier)-[:SUPPLIES]->(p:Product)<-[:ORDERS]-(o:CustomerOrder) WHERE o.delay > 0 WITH s, count(o) AS delayed RETURN s.name, delayed ORDER BY delayed DESC LIMIT 5;

instruction: Show orders delayed by more than 7 days.

instruction: Count shipments by transport mode.
cypher: MATCH (sh:Shipment)-[:USES_TRANSPORT]->(t:TransportMode) RETURN t.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC;

instruction: Which warehouse handles the most shipments?
cypher: MATCH (w:Warehouse)<-[:SHIPPED_FROM]-(sh:Shipment) RETURN w.name, count(sh) ORDER BY count(sh) DESC LIMIT 1;

instruction: Count shipments by transport mode.

instruction: Top 5 products by total ordered quantity.
